              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was made from a thin copper backing,",
                " 0.005 cm thick, on to which was evaporated a layer of",
                "titanium 0.0025 g/cm**2 thick. The tritium gas was",
                "absorbed into this titanium layer. The total volume of",
                "tritium absorbed into the target was 1.0 ml.",
                "For angular distributions, a tritium loaded target",
                "placed at the centre of a 30 cm diameter scattering",
                "chamber, for the excitations functions a similar",
                "tritium loaded target placed normal to the beam at the",
                "centre of a 70 cm diameter scattering chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
